{"article_id":"qBSrD3ee8Mx3vfhF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The U.S. Senate on Thursday overwhelmingly approved the U.S.-Mexico-Canada Agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"sending the pact to President Donald Trump for signature","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"just a day after he inked a high-profile trade deal with China .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"Approved","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"just as the chamber is preparing for Trump ' s impeachment trial ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"senators voted 89 to 10","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to pass the deal ,","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"which replaces the North American Free Trade Agreement .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Trump has repeatedly slammed NAFTA ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"blaming the 26-year-old pact","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"for sending American jobs abroad ,","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and had threatened to pull the U.S. out of that three-way agreement","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"absent any changes .","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"The new deal makes changes to trading rules among the three countries .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Among them are higher thresholds","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"for how much of an automobile must be made in North America","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"in order to trade vehicles duty-free ; greater access to Canada ' s dairy market ; and easier unionization for Mexican workers .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"USMCA got strong buy-in from Democrats","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"after they won changes","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"strengthening its labor , environmental and other provisions .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Just one Republican ,","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"Pat Toomey of Pennsylvania , voted against it .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"The senator has charged","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that it will diminish trade .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"Passage by the Senate on Thursday followed a 385-41 vote in the House of Representatives last month .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"See :","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"' Outdated ' Nafta one step away from demise","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"after House passes new trade deal with Canada , Mexico .","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Before signing the China deal on Wednesday ,","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"Trump said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"the USMCA should be approved shortly","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"and \" we ' ll talk about that next week. \"","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"Touting the China agreement on Twitter ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"the president said ,","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"\" USMCA next ! \"","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"One of the greatest trade deals","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"ever made !","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"Also good for China and our long term relationship .","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"250 Billion Dollars will be coming back to our Country ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"and we are now in a great position for a Phase Two start .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"There has never been anything like this in U.S. history !","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"USMCA NEXT !","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"January 16 , 2020","depth":5},{"id":45,"text":"Mexico has passed the USMCA","depth":4},{"id":46,"text":"but Canada must also ratify it","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"for it to take effect .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"That could come in late January ,","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"when the House of Commons reconvenes .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"The USMCA vote came","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"as the Senate is gearing up for Trump ' s impeachment trial","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"and as voters are preparing for the start of the presidential primary election season .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Sen. Bernie Sanders ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"who is No . 2 in an average of national surveys for the Democratic presidential nomination ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"voted against the deal .","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"Fellow White House hopeful Sen. Elizabeth Warren backed it .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Warren ranks third nationally ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"according to an average of polls by RealClearPolitics .","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"Now read :","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Sanders says","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"he won ' t vote for USMCA","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"despite ' modest improvement '","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"it makes .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"U.S. stock benchmarks DJIA , +0.92 % reached new record intraday highs Thursday ,","depth":3},{"id":65,"text":"following the Wednesday signing of the China trade deal and healthy U.S. economic data","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"released Thursday .","depth":4},{"id":67,"text":"See :","depth":3},{"id":68,"text":"Stock-market benchmarks surge to new records","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"as investors ride optimism of U.S.-China trade accord .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":139,"left":133,"right":138,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":133,"left":114,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":97,"right":113,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":93,"right":96,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":93,"left":82,"right":92,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":72,"right":81,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":71,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":81,"left":76,"right":80,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":73,"right":75,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":5,"right":74,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":8,"right":79,"relat